<A>__{close on edward, smiling nervously. his head is tilted to the side, and as we pull back, we see why: he's holding it in a massive lion's open mouth. the beast's sharp teeth are just poking his skin. if the lion so much as flinches, edward is dead. the crowd applauds, which makes the lion antsy. which makes edward antsier.}
<C>__{edward }
<D>__{from that moment on, i did everything mr. calloway asked, and a lot of things he didn't. i'd go three days without stopping to eat, and four days without sleeping.}
